<h3 id="oj-mystat-">oj mystat <option></option></h3>
<h4 id="about-8">About</h4>
<p>Use <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">oj mystat &lt;option&gt;</code> to view your latest 20 submissions of this contest, each of the submission has the specific ID.</p>
<h4 id="usage-8">Usage</h4>
<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">oj mystat</code> only required one argument to execute.</p>
<h5 id="option">option</h5>
<p>Here we have two options:</p>
<ol>
  <li>assign_no represents your assign number like <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">hw1</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">hw2</code> according to your updates. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">oj-cli</code> will prompt <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Invalid Assign Number!</code> if the input assign number has not opened and give valid assign numbers.</li>
  <li>IDx is the specific ID that <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">oj mystat &lt;hwx&gt;</code> gives you, here you can see details of this submition.
    <h4 id="note">Note</h4>
    <p>The ID will only update if you type <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">oj mystat &lt;hwx&gt;</code></p>
  </li>
</ol>

